snippet.textDisplay:
I think this song (In the lyrics) represent very well the reason why LOONA doesn't have a lot of popularity in Korea and i think is because LOONA in the majority of their songs doesn't follow the trends and they experiment with different sounds. And like the song say they're "Bad" because they don't play it safe wich made the Knetz to think they are weird because they don't do songs with trending sounds.

And actually this is how real world is. If you are unique and don't follow the rules that the society thinks are good, you become a "weirdo" or people that go in a bad way. But in reality we are more Free than anybody else, and LOONA make us embrace that and show us how to make it our strength and embrace ourselves.

And that is why they are my favorite group of this generation, you can feel stronger and free listening to their music, so I hope the Koreans stop sleeping on LOONA because they are the most unique group around right now.
